methodBody: public Map < String , String > getEffectiveConverterMap ( ) { Map < String , String > effectiveMap = new HashMap < String , String > ( ) ; // add the least specific map fist Map < String , String > defaultMap = getDefaultConverterMap ( ) ; if ( defaultMap != null ) { effectiveMap . putAll ( defaultMap ) ; } // contextMap is more specific than the default map Context context = getContext ( ) ; if ( context != null ) { @ SuppressWarnings ( "unchecked" ) Map < String , String > contextMap = ( Map < String , String > ) context . getObject ( CoreConstants . PATTERN_RULE_REGISTRY ) ; if ( contextMap != null ) { effectiveMap . putAll ( contextMap ) ; } } return effectiveMap ; }
